{"type":"text","timestamp":1775848141509,"sessionID":"ses_287342fa6ffeeSqqqPAigKo80v","part":{"id":"prt_d78cc20b9001MhL4akjZz5Tfky","messageID":"msg_d78cc0b30001PFSetPWUeRWwdP","sessionID":"ses_287342fa6ffeeSqqqPAigKo80v","type":"text","text":"Based on the tasks.md and existing implementation files:\n\n## AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 Summary\n\n### Completed (✓)\n- **Phase 1**: Core Infrastructure — `config.go`, `server.go`, `backend.go`, `proxy.go` all implemented\n- **Phase 2**: Kubernetes Informers — `informer.go` with handlers for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRs\n- **Phase 3**: Routing Logic — `route.go` with path prefix and header-based routing\n- **Phase 4**: Health Checking — `health.go` with periodic checks, unhealthy removal, recovery\n- **Phase 5**: Connection Pooling — built into `proxy.go` via httputil.ReverseProxy\n- **Phase 6**: Middleware — `ratelimit.go`, `auth.go`, `logging.go` all implemented\n- **Phase 7**: Metrics — `metrics.go` with Prometheus metrics\n- All test files created (`*_test.go`)\n\n### Deferred\n- **Phase 8: Verification** — `go build` and `go test` verification not explicitly confirmed completed in task list (tasks 8.1-8.3 remain unchecked)","time":{"start":1775848141506,"end":1775848141506}}}
